@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wbsqez(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((v0 * (v0 + 0.15 - v0 + 0.93)) - wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.30)))
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.24)) + v2)
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v2 + 0.97)) + (v2 - wp.abs(v1 + 0.61)))
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.24) / 0.97) + 0.20)
    v0 = ((v1 * (v0 + 0.21 + tmp + 0.52)) - wp.exp((v0 + 0.18 + v1 + 0.41)))
    data[tid] = v0
